                                                <strong>Mission</strong>
                                            </h3>
                                            <p align="justify">

                                            St. Dominic Savio College is an educational institution with a primary mission of ensuring the TOTAL DEVELOPMENT OF PERSONS. Adopting the philosophy of St. Dominic Savio – the patron Saints of the youth – as the cornerstone of education, SDSC aims to produce future leaders of businesses and stewards of society who are equipped to cope with the educational, business, scientific and technological advances. It aims to muster individuals who epitomize the highest ideals of service to the community, the country and the world –at-large. SDSC bears the responsibility of meeting the needs, arousing the interest and the inherent skills and developing of its students. It promotes relevant education and academic excellence as well as positive attitudes, values and skills needed in the realization of individual, local and national development. 

SDSC believes that education in its highest form in nit the mere transfer of knowledge but a reminded to every student of the eternal verities and the principles of life that make it possible to live fully and happily being in communion with others.</p>
